attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Classic Realty NW - Ely

data.description: 4 bedroom, 1.75 bath home on a corner lot with an attached garage, back deck and a screen porch.  Features include: Spacious kitchen with wood cabinets, appliances & open to the dining room.  Living room with carpeting & large window.  2 main floor bedrooms with hardwood floors.  Main floor 3/4 bath with walk-in shower.  Lower level features a rec room with a bar, 2 bedrooms, full bathroom & a spacious laundry / utility room.  Exterior features include: 2 stall detached garage, newer roof, wood siding, back deck and a  screen porch all located on a corner lot.
